      "step_type": "reasoning",
      "content": "**Structural alerts relevant to CYP2D6 inhibition**\n- **Tertiary amine + aromatic ring(s)** is a classic CYP2D6 inhibitor motif (many CYP2D6 inhibitors are \u201cbasic + aromatic/hydrophobic\u201d).\n- Not a quinidine scaffold, but **fits the general CYP2D6 pharmacophore** (basic center + hydrophobic/aromatic region).",
